            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-d28caa8f-1c37-41d8-97a2-9fe2cd6eb3a2">
                Mr. M. Follick  (Loughborough)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-d28caa8f-1c37-41d8-97a2-9fe2cd6eb3a2" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
