    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">Abolish them, they said.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-d28caa8f-1c37-41d8-97a2-9fe2cd6eb3a2" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1954-02-25/debates/48b7a6fa-412a-47b1-9d45-d1c8dcac4474/ForeignMinistersConferenceBerlin#contribution-d28caa8f-1c37-41d8-97a2-9fe2cd6eb3a2">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
