<p class="">Now tell us what the Germans did.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-a0a44049-35a4-4d88-bb5b-d0bc4d8cfcb2" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
