                Mr. Stewart
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-5458b126-506c-41af-8afe-b1d37736d71b" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1954-02-25/debates/48b7a6fa-412a-47b1-9d45-d1c8dcac4474/ForeignMinistersConferenceBerlin#contribution-5458b126-506c-41af-8afe-b1d37736d71b">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
